ed Over 25 Million Dollars\n| data-sort-value=\"Pasek, Benj\" | Benj Pasek and Justin Paul\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/music/news/guild-of-music-supervisors-awards-nominations-1202661480/ |title=Sufjan Stevens, ''Greatest Showman'', ''Girls'' Among Guild of Music Supervisors Awards Nominees |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|date=January 11, 2018 |accessdate=January 12, 2018|author=''Variety'' staff}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Song/Recording Created for a Film\n| data-sort-value=\"This Is Me\" | \"This Is Me\" \u2013 Benj Pasek and Justin Paul\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Heartland Film Festival]]\n| December 31, 2017\n| Truly Moving Picture Award\n| data-sort-value=\"Gracey, Michael\" | [[Michael Gracey]]\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://heartlandfilm.org/tmpa/ |title=Truly Moving Picture Award |publisher=Heartland Film |accessdate=February 10, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| [[Nickelodeon Kids' Choice Awards|Kids' Choice Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[2018 Kids' Choice Awards|March 24, 2018]]\n| [[Kids' Choice Award for Favorite Movie|Favorite Movie]]\n| data-sort-value=\"Greatest Showman, The\" | ''The Greatest Showman''\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2018/03/nickelodeon-kids-choice-awards-2018-winners-the-complete-list-1202352942/ |title=Nickelodeon Kids' Choice Awards 2018 Winners \u2013 The Complete List |last=Haring |first=Bruce |work=Deadline Hollywood|date=March 24, 2018 |accessdate=June 23, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| Favorite Movie Actress\n| [[Zendaya]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Make-Up Artists and Hair Stylists Guild]]\n| February 24, 2018\n| Feature Motion Picture: Best Period and/or Character Makeup\n| data-sort-value=\"Ledermann, Nicki\" | Nicki Ledermann, Tania Ribalow and Sunday Englis\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=